highlights.text: Hov1 has the most spots on Top Songs Sweden. “Förr nu & forever” is the highest at #9.
“Svindlande höjder” by Håkan Hellström is the highest new entry on Top Songs Sweden at #45.
“Babblarnas vaggvisa” by Babblarna has been on Top Songs Sweden the longest, at 350 weeks straight.
“Strövtåg i hembygden” by Mando Diao is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Sweden, up 49 spots at #119.
